title: Medaka Box – Digital Colored Comics
author: NisiOisiN
description: Kurokami Medaka, a first year, is elected as Student Council President, and the first thing she does is establish a suggestion box, later dubbed by students the “Medaka Box.” Medaka encourages students to submit any problem to the box without hesitation and promises to take on any issue from anyone.
